dct_description_sm: Relief shown by hachures and spot heights. Also shows plantations and subdivisions. "Hawaii Territory survey, Walter E. Wall, surveyor ... 1903." "Specially prepared map of the County of Kauai for governor's annual report, illustrating conditions as of June 30, 1906." From: Report of the governor of the Territory of Hawaii to the Secretary of the Interior, 1906. Washington : Government Printing Office, 1906.
dct_publisher_sm: [Washington, D.C. : Government Printing Office], 1906 (Washington, D.C. : Andrew & Graham Co., Lithographers)
